To install the ingwer software please edit the installer file install.pl.

For successfully installing and running the software, the following prerequisites have to be fulfilled:

- web server with PHP, Perl and MySQL data base
- installed part-of-speech tagger "TreeTagger" with German library (http://www.cis.uni-muenchen.de/~schmid/tools/TreeTagger/)

If you want to use the interface to the Open Corpus Workbench you need additionally:

- CWB and CQPWeb: http://cwb.sourceforge.net/download.php

